{"tid":1062033,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"海鮮與港女的微妙關係","createTime":"2019-03-14T23:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T14:08:52.000Z","uid":213418,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a04f175e437039d85612cf6aa5ec72e460d95b1f","tid":1062033,"uid":213418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T23:08:47.000Z","msg":"由細食海鮮食到大 領悟到一樣嘢 覺唔覺會食海鮮嘅女仔通常都唔係港女 例如:食蝦，蟹，佢地唔會奉子咁要你幫手剝殼 而係自己搞得掂 食魚唔怕lur骨同唔怕腥<br />\n<br />\n呢啲女仔如果岀嚟同屋企人食飯 一定唔會怕失禮 唔會揀飲擇食 又厭腥又厭多骨又咩又咩咁 之後對住啲餸西口西面<br />\n<br />\n正評:同意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n負評:唔撚柒同意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6f816ff30b3ca0953508ba24e7b883a8155a81","tid":1062033,"uid":164387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T23:12:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73839bbda7071c265331fdd70215d72ba2db83dd","tid":1062033,"uid":228131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de6f816ff30b3ca0953508ba24e7b883a8155a81","tid":1062033,"uid":164387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T23:12:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T23:14:30.000Z","msg":"鹹魚唔算海鮮，係乾貨"},{"pid":"14f0e0a72511406079f402ef7075f0f6e9e7d4a2","tid":1062033,"uid":164387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T23:20:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88875e8edb5c7e47a50db39908a897423b48e59c","tid":1062033,"uid":42146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T23:24:58.000Z","msg":"um...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d5bb3cd8fc5ff8d27821a4e2d22873a4e6e085","tid":1062033,"uid":48286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T00:26:06.000Z","msg":"投乜撚嘢票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f508740942a9ec57793470f7eb5f57aeb46eaf","tid":1062033,"uid":222791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"